@startuml
title Job Application Platform - Context Diagram

actor "Applicant" as Applicant
actor "Recruiter" as Recruiter
actor "Operator / ted" as Operator

rectangle "Modern Web Platform - Python" {
  component "FastAPI Job Application API" as API
  database "JSON / CSV Storage\nFuture PostgreSQL" as Store
}

Recruiter --> API : Create/Update/Delete Jobs
Applicant --> API : Search/View Jobs
Operator --> API : Health Check / Validate
API --> Store : Read/Write Jobs

@enduml
